These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
House: tower, townhouse, modern, art-deco, cottage
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, siglo, montecristo, aristoff, pall-mall
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, superhero, drama, sports, action
City: boston, edinburgh, san-francisco, marseilles, miami
 1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is the cottage house##1
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is the aristoff-smoker##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is the townhouse house##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the tower house is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
10. the art-deco house is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is the person traveling to boston##1
12. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| House         | townhouse  | tower    | art-deco | modern    | cottage  |
| Cigar   | siglo  | ritmeester | montecristo | aristoff | pall-mall  |
| Movie-Genre           | crime     | action     | sports  | superhero   | drama    |
| City         | san-francisco | marseilles    | edinburgh | boston  | miami |

