.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, davidoff, ritmeester, siglo, blend
5 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, horse, hamster, cat
5 different games are played: billiard, poker, domino, monopoly, go
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, juice, tea, milk
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking juice is the person playing poker##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is the person playing domino##1
 9. the person drinking tea is the ritmeester-smoker##1
10. the davidoff-smoker is in the middle##1
11. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
12. the ritmeester-smoker is the owner of the rabbit##1
13. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Cigar          | ritmeester        | blend | davidoff     | siglo      | prince  |
| Pet           | rabbit   | horse | cat    | hamster | fish |
| Game   | domino | monopoly     | go | billiard    | poker  |
| Beverage   | tea     | 7up | iced-tea    | milk      | juice    |

