.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, amber, brown, azure
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, alhambra, cain, oliveros, vegafina
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie, animation, fantasy, family
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, october, may, july, april
 1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 2. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is in the middle##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the fonseca-smoker##1
12. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
13. the person who likes brown is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Color      | brown          | amber  | fuchsia       | purple     | azure      |
| Cigar         | alhambra | vegafina | oliveros  | cain   | fonseca    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie        | family | thriller | fantasy    | animation   |
| Birthday     | december   | may | april      | october | july |

