.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
5 different pets are kept: horse, ferret, mouse, goldfish, bird
There are 5 different nationalities: american, german, turkish, australian, canadian
5 different games are played: billiard, canasta, whist, mah-jongg, monopoly
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, puzzles, sudoku, chess
 1. the german is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the american is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 3. the person playing canasta is the german##1
 4. the person playing billiard is the american##1
 5. the turkish is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the american##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the canadian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is in the middle##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
10. the owner of the bird is the person playing whist##1
11. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Pet          | goldfish        | horse       | mouse | ferret   | bird  |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish | german | american   | australian |
| Game   | mah-jongg         | monopoly     | canasta | billiard | whist     |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing        | filmmaking        | chess    | sudoku    | puzzles      |

