There 5 different types of food: lettuce, banana, apricot, corn, plum
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, american, turkish, pakistani, spanish
There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, white, purple, ebony, yellow
The people have 5 different hobbies: woodworking, filmmaking, chess, writing, collecting
 1. the american is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 2. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
 3. the pakistani is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 5. the italian is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the american is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the italian##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating banana##1
11. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the spanish##1
12. the turkish is the person who likes ebony##1
13. the spanish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Food      | lettuce      | banana       | plum         | corn  | apricot |
| Nationality   | turkish  | pakistani | american | italian  | spanish  |
| Color   | ebony    | white    | ivory        | yellow | purple     |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | chess      | woodworking       | writing   | collecting   |

