.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
House: art-deco, townhouse, victorian, futuristic, cottage
There 5 different types of food: kale, cauliflower, cranberry, asparagus, pomegranate
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, game, montecristo, fonseca, vegafina
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, mechanic, software-developer, photographer, scientist
 1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the scientist##1
 3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the photographer##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
 6. the mechanic is on the left of the cottage house##1
 7. the townhouse house is the designer##1
 8. the victorian house is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the game-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the havana-smoker is the person eating pomegranate##1
11. the photographer is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
12. the cottage house is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
13. the futuristic house is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| House   | townhouse      | futuristic | victorian  | cottage    | art-deco |
| Food   | asparagus     | pomegranate     | cauliflower | kale      | cranberry      |
| Cigar           | montecristo       | havana     | game     | vegafina     | fonseca   |
| Job         | designer | photographer | mechanic  | scientist | software-developer   |

