.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
City: venice, liverpool, paris, rome, boston
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, malaysian, thai, italian, mexican
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, biathlon, snowboarding, volleyball, baseball
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, card-games, biathloning, board-games, traveling
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the mexican is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is biathloning is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the malaysian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the russian is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
12. the thai is the person traveling to boston##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| City      | paris | boston    | liverpool   | rome   | venice |
| Nationality   | russian    | thai   | mexican | italian | malaysian  |
| Sport           | biathlon     | volleyball | snowboarding   | baseball | weightlifting   |
| Hobby     | card-games  | traveling   | cooking    | board-games   | biathloning |

