.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There 5 different types of food: onion, cucumber, radish, pear, tomato
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, amaryllis, daisy, bellflower, balloon-flower
5 different games are played: poker, monopoly, canasta, backgammon, domino
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving, hiking, gardening, woodworking
 1. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is the person playing domino##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating onion##1
10. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is in the middle##1
13. the person playing poker is the person eating pear##1
14. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Food      | cucumber | pear   | radish    | onion       | tomato |
| Flower   | daisy           | amaryllis   | balloon-flower   | bellflower       | begonia  |
| Game   | monopoly       | poker | canasta | backgammon     | domino   |
| Hobby     | hiking    | skydiving   | gardening   | video-games | woodworking   |

 